    "Only 4 of them in 741, namely less than 0.54%, have a strong correlation, stated by |ρ X,Y | > 0.7.",
    "Thus, option (iv), namely considering output variables singularly, is the most meaningful and was chosen.",
    "This choice also gave the possibility to use a different ML algorithm for the prediction of each variable, improving the overall accuracy.",
